# Push Image to Docker Hub

Today I pushed my Docker image to Docker Hub.

Command used:

docker push username/myimage:1.0

Result:
Image successfully uploaded to Docker Hub.

Learning:
I learned how to share my Docker image online.


# Pull Image from Docker Hub

Today I learned how to pull an image from Docker Hub.

Command used:

docker pull username/myimage:1.0

docker run username/myimage:1.0

Learning:
I understood how to download and run images from Docker Hub.
